        "ai_gen_block_4b89c2e_8UUd9w": {
          "type": "ai_gen_block_4b89c2e",
          "name": "Text",
          "settings": {
            "text_content": "<p>For over six decades, Janardhana Silk House has stood as a treasured destination for the finest silk sarees, bringing together India’s most exquisite handmade weaves under one roof. Showcasing an extraordinary range—from rich Kanjivaram and regal Banarasi to vibrant Patola, elegant Mysore silk, graceful crepe, and timeless cottons—each creation reflects the beauty of tradition shaped for the modern woman.</p><p>Every saree is handwoven with the finest silk threads and brought to life through masterful craftsmanship, intricate embroidery, and thoughtfully curated colors and designs. Whether it is a grand wedding, a festive celebration, or an intimate gathering, the collection offers a perfect expression for every occasion.</p><p>Rooted in heritage since 1952, the house blends enduring Indian artistry with contemporary style, guided by generations of knowledge, care, and passion. With a deep understanding of its patrons and their evolving tastes, Janardhana Silk House has become more than a store—it is a cherished family tradition passed from one generation to the next.</p><p>Here, every creation is a promise: what you dream is lovingly brought to life.</p>",
            "font_family": "assistant_n4",
            "font_size": 16,
            "line_height": 1.5,
            "text_alignment": "left",
